N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4203.6 - Retirement

State Regulations

Each member of the commission upon retirement shall have
the title of honorary steward in recognition of his services, with such duties, rights and privileges as may be specified by the commission. Notes
